20
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,910
There's something

21
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,560
I've been wondering for a long time.

22
00:05:21,750 --> 00:05:22,830
In your life,

23
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,560
besides yourself,

24
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:28,590
who have you truly loved?

25
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,200
