26
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:32,320
and that was your mother.

27
00:05:33,750 --> 00:05:34,670
Really?

28
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:36,000
Your mother

29
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,470
being crippled

30
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,240
was just an accident.

31
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,390
I never intended to harm her.

32
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,640
That night at Shili Stop,

33
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:49,640
