34
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:54,710
and I was heartbroken too.

35
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:58,470
I was crying as I let her go.

36
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,710
For all these years,

37
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:04,030
I often dream about the beautiful scene

38
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,510
when your mother and I

39
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:10,120
first met.

40
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:13,150
I loved her so much,

41
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,280
but

42
00:06:17,830 --> 00:06:21,200
I had to personally kill her.

43
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:22,430
Hanyan,

44
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,390
