45
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:25,870
You should understand

46
00:06:25,870 --> 00:06:27,200
what it means to be helpless.

47
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,640
Since that year

48
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,320
when Eunuch Pei found your grandfather,

49
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,070
the gears of fate

50
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,830
began to turn,

51
00:06:35,510 --> 00:06:36,510
pulling

52
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:38,390
all of us

53
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:41,150
into the whirlpool.

54
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:47,070
