55
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:49,030
until I arrived at this point.

56
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,510
Saying the softest words

57
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:55,200
while doing the most ruthless things.

58
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,710
You've never changed.

59
00:06:59,270 --> 00:07:00,270
Hanyan,

60
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:02,510
if right now,

61
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,350
you knew Fu Yunxi

62
