was plotting to usurp the throne,

63
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:08,310
you knew

64
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:12,680
he would surely fail,

65
00:07:13,270 --> 00:07:15,030
bringing ruin to your entire family,

66
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,360
and I handed you the knife,

67
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,680
would you kill him?

68
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,710
You can't answer me?

69
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:25,350
No.

70
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,390
I suppose

71
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,950
I would kill him too,

72
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:33,150
but I wouldn't pin the blame

73
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:35,040
on a child

74
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,760
or stir up disputes
in the inner chambers

75
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:38,880
to cover up my own crimes.

76
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:41,200
I wouldn't ignore the kindness
as a human

77
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:44,120
just for my own survival,

78
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:46,000
killing one innocent person
after another

79
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:48,630
while putting on a false, virtuous face,

80
00:07:48,630 --> 00:07:50,350
and trying to shift

81
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,240
all the blame onto fate.

82
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,000
I dare to admit

83
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:55,710
the things I've done,

84
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,830
but you don't.

85
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,440
That's the biggest difference
between us.

86
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:03,120
Actually, we're the same.

87
00:08:03,430 --> 00:08:05,720
We just want

88
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,200
a warm and harmonious home.

89
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:08,430
What do you think

90
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,560
makes a home?

91
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,870
A table full of delicious dishes
is in front of you,

92
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,950
but you can't even have a single bite.

93
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:18,950
You have no trust in your family.

94
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:20,320
How could someone like you

95
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:22,200
have a home?

96
00:08:22,630 --> 00:08:24,240
You don't know what love is,

97
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,200
so naturally,
you don't know what home is.

98
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,800
We're like carrying a snowball
down a hill.

99
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,200
When you can't bear the weight,

100
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,790
you let it roll bigger and bigger

101
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:38,280
until it crashes onto my back.

102
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,630
But I won't let go.

103
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,040
I will carry it

104
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:44,230
until I walk off the cliff.

105
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:49,230
I can sever all the harm

106
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:50,750
and pain

107
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:54,550
passed down
from the previous generation,

108
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:57,160
and I'll never let the children
suffer that harm again.

109
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:58,520
But you can't do that.

110
00:08:58,790 --> 00:09:01,200
You only bring more harm and pain.

111
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,830
It's fine that you don't admit it.

112
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:08,630
I don't need to waste more words on you.

113
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:14,160
As we agreed before,

114
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,440
